  <title>机床数据输入/输出程序</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading3">机床数据输入/输出程序</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text style="font-weight:bold;">输出程序</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">将外置卡或 USB 闪盘插入主操作面板上的 PCMCIA 端口或 USB 端口。(参照<link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="false" type="topiclink" href="SRAM-Backup" anchor="Fig3.5" target="_blank" style="color:#0000ff;">图 3.5）</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">NC 参数备份程序</text></para>
    <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[SYSTEM]</text>功能键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[+]</text>软键直至显示<text style="font-weight:bold;">[PARAM]</text>，然后按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[PARAM]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[OPRT]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[+]</text>软键直至显示<text style="font-weight:bold;">[FOUTPUT]</text>，然后按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[FOUTPUT]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[ALL]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[EXEC]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px;">数据输出到存储卡。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">螺距误差补偿数据备份程序</text></para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[SYSTEM]</text>功能键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[+]</text>软键直至显示<text style="font-weight:bold;">[音调]</text>，然后按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[音调]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[OPRT]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[+]</text>软键直至显示<text style="font-weight:bold;">[FOUTPUT]</text>，然后按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[FOUTPUT]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[ALL]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[EXEC]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px;">数据输出到存储卡。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">自定义宏变量备份程序</text></para>
    <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[SYSTEM]</text>功能键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[+]</text>软键直至显示<text style="font-weight:bold;">[MACRO]</text>，然后按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[MACRO]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[OPRT]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[+]</text>软键直至显示<text style="font-weight:bold;">[FOUTPUT]</text>，然后按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[FOUTPUT]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[ALL]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[EXEC]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px;">数据输出到存储卡。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; page-break-before:always;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">刀具偏置备份程序</text></para>
    <list id="3" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[SYSTEM]</text>功能键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[+]</text>软键直至显示<text style="font-weight:bold;">[OFFSET]</text>，然后按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[OFFSET]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[OPRT]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[+]</text>软键直至显示<text style="font-weight:bold;">[FOUTPUT]</text>，然后按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[FOUTPUT]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[ALL]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[EXEC]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px;">数据输出到存储卡。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">工作抵消备份程序</text></para>
    <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[SYSTEM]</text>功能键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[+]</text>软键直至显示<text style="font-weight:bold;">[WORK</text>&#32;<text style="font-weight:bold;">]</text>，然后按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[WORK]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[OPRT]</text>软键。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[+]</text>软键直至显示<text style="font-weight:bold;">[FOUTPUT]</text>，然后按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[FOUTPUT]</text>。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-29px; margin-left:29px; line-height:1.50;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[ALL]</text>软键。</li>
